@host = http://localhost:5001

###

### SignalR negotiate for board hub
GET {{host}}/hubs/board/negotiate?negotiateVersion=1
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv AUTH_TOKEN}}
Response: { connectionToken: "..." }

###

### SignalR negotiate for presence hub
GET {{host}}/hubs/presence/negotiate?negotiateVersion=1
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Board mutation → BoardEvent broadcast
### POST /api/projects/{projectId}/cards → BoardHub.OnBoardEvent(BoardAction.Created)
### POST /api/projects/{projectId}/columns/{columnId}/cards/{cardId}/move → BoardHub.OnBoardEvent(BoardAction.Moved)
### Archive project → BoardHub.OnBoardEvent(BoardAction.Archived)
